| FSM state | SRAM 1 | SRAM 2 | SRAM 3 (Q/AO) | SRAM 4 (K) | SRAM 5 (V) | SRAM 6 (QKM) |
|-----------|--------|--------|---------------|------------|------------|--------------|
| (care) LOAD_X → `Sram_x` | W | – | – | – | – | – |
| QKV (linear) | R (`Sram_x`) | – | W (`Sram_q`) | W | W | – |
